   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the <uicontrol>Main Menu</uicontrol>, select <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>System Control</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Charge mode</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> using the UP/DOWN keys and the ENTER key. </p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Charge mode:      FloatUbat: 440.3V  438  VIbat:+004.2A  007.2A</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Charge mode:      CyclicUbat: 440.3V  438  VIbat:+004.2A  007.2A↓</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
               <p>
                  <uicontrol>Cyclic</uicontrol> charge mode has a second
page that shows the configured period and charge time.</p>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the ENTER key to start modifying the parameter values.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press the UP/DOWN keys to modify the parameter values and
press the ENTER key to confirm modification.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table outputclass="font:10">
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Charge mode:↕      FloatUbat: 440.3V  438  VIbat:+004.2A  007.2A</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
      </ol>
